function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(idNPC, S_ANIM_PANIC_IDLE)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idNPC, S_ANIM_PANIC)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONV_WARNING, idNPC)
end

function Start()
	if Hydra.ActorGetGender(idNPC) == "F" then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idNPC, "Play_QUE_Generic_Scream_Female")
	else
		Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idNPC, "Play_QUE_Generic_Scream_Male")
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idNPC, S_PWR_TRANSFORM)

	Hydra.Wait(2)
	T_GORE = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "GORE")
	
	for i, idGore in ipairs(T_GORE) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idGore) then
			Hydra.ActorEnable(idGore)
		end
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	--Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idSummonFX, 1)
	
	Hydra.Wait(6)
	for i, idGore in ipairs(T_GORE) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idGore) then
			Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idGore, 6)
		end
	end
end
